channel.name: BBC One NL
channel.title: Strictly Come Dancing
channel.desc: The mood is tense in the ballroom as our couples wait for the result of the latest public vote. In honour of icons week, our professionals take on the one and only Britney for their latest group performance, and Hollywood star Rachel Zegler performs the iconic song Don't Cry for Me Argentina. As the two bottom-placed couples go head-to-head in the dance-off, who will make it through to the annual Halloween spectacular next weekend?
